casebody.data:
Toledo Bar Association v. Anderson.

[Cite as Toledo Bar Assn. v. Anderson (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 209.]

(No. 91-1253 Submitted September 11, 1991 Decided December 11, 1991.) *211Joseph L. Wittenberg and Edward J. McCormick, Jr., for relator. Delores Joan Anderson, pro se. Per Curiam.

We agree with the board’s findings and recommendation. Accordingly, we order that respondent be indefinitely suspended from the practice of law in Ohio. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
